Key Match Events: Utah Jazz head coach Will Hardy benched Keyonte George in the third quarter due to defense concerns.
Isaiah Collier played a career-high 26 minutes, contributing four points, eight assists, and two steals.
Post-Match Reflections: Will Hardy emphasized that benching Keyonte George was about reinforcing defensive habits, not punishment.
Keyonte George scored 9 points on 4/12 shooting, with five rebounds and three assists, despite not starting the second half.
